      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is preserved in showroom condition, exhibiting an impeccable finish and a pristine interior that reflects meticulous ownership. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards of the discerning collector. This is an investment-grade opportunity for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
