    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been my baby\u2014always kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. It\u2019s in truly spectacular shape, looking and driving just like it did the day it left the showroom. If you're looking for something that's been pampered and is ready for a new home, this is the one! I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see how pristine it really is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
