    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly investment-grade vehicle that can only be described as a time capsule. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its flawless factory paint which retains a deep, mirror-like luster free of any stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. The interior is equally pristine; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the cabin still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every toggle, switch, and digital interface functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service portfolio with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time by certified technicians. It has never seen inclement weather and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. For the discerning collector who accepts nothing less than a showroom-perfect example, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
